{"tid":2123740,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【繙譯問題】Switch《紙片瑪利歐》中日版字幕大不同 中文版飛走「人權」加「自由」","createTime":"2020-07-25T01:59:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T08:47:26.000Z","uid":22675,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"474d28fee5b88addbe7bbf8061843394991a8185","tid":2123740,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T01:59:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TIYOXhxPtTmrxDcj5r3W8VlA80g=/640x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LOEEHCZKH4CSWY5IIEJSESFMJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTIYOXhxPtTmrxDcj5r3W8VlA80g%3D%2F640x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLOEEHCZKH4CSWY5IIEJSESFMJM.jpg&h=cbf64cd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2QcDCDQDXLexhiauknVZ9O2TzTg=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CEZIMW73ER36BYRYDRNKVDWWBE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2QcDCDQDXLexhiauknVZ9O2TzTg%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCEZIMW73ER36BYRYDRNKVDWWBE.jpg&h=02a6d2c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現在很多遊戲都會推出中文版，不過地區語文有異，對白意思可能隨時會「lost in translation」。近日就有台灣網民發現Switch新遊戲《Paper Mario The Origami King》（紙片瑪利歐：摺紙國王）中的台詞中日版大有不同，日文版寫到「人權」和「自由」，來到中文版則變成了「平整的外表」和「平靜的生活」。<br />\n<br />\n事件在網上廣受機迷討論，有些人認為中文繙譯有自我審查的嫌疑，亦有人覺得中、英、日版3個版本的說法各有分別。我們先來了解一下故事的前文後理，《Paper Mario》中出現的角色無論是瑪利歐或是「蘑菇人」（中文是奇諾比奧、英文是Toad）都是紙製的，故事講到蘑菇人受到的摺紙狂徒欺負，將他們摺到面目全非，因此蘑菇人向瑪利歐控訴。日文說蘑菇人要有人權和自由，英文是說「Toads have rights！This is Toad abuse！」，大意是說：蘑菇人也有人權，這是欺凌蘑菇人！中文版的「平整的外表」和「平靜的生活」大致上也表達了控訴的意思，但繙譯水平如何就由讀者自行定斷了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200724/ZO7BP2JJ7TNCKYZXE5MBQGRCXU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_gadgetguy.appleseed&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=square_link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200724%2FZO7BP2JJ7TNCKYZXE5MBQGRCXU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_gadgetguy.appleseed%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dsquare_link_post&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=574b85c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200724%2FZO7BP2JJ7TNCKYZXE5MBQGRCXU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_gadgetguy.appleseed%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dsquare_link_post&h=e8b82670\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200724/ZO7BP2JJ7TNCKYZXE5MBQGRCXU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_gadgetguy.appleseed&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=square_link_post</a>"},{"pid":"478739a254d3cafbea238c924836d7277f99971f","tid":2123740,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T02:03:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200724/ZO7BP2JJ7TNCKYZXE5MBQGRCXU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_gadgetguy.appleseed&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=square_link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200724%2FZO7BP2JJ7TNCKYZXE5MBQGRCXU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_gadgetguy.appleseed%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dsquare_link_post&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=574b85c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200724%2FZO7BP2JJ7TNCKYZXE5MBQGRCXU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_gadgetguy.appleseed%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dsquare_link_post&h=e8b82670\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.l